"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?1/21/1363?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Teen sexuality (The Basics)",
"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?1/12/1218?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Acne (The Basics)",
"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?3/12/3266?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: My child is short (The Basics)",
"      </a>",
"     </p>",
"     <p>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?35/8/35973?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Adolescent sexuality (Beyond the Basics)",
"      </a>",
"     </p>",
